    {
      "id": "9c123075_b173c445",
      "file_path": "cps-ri/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/spi/impl/CpsDataPersistenceServiceImpl.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 251,
      "message": "agreed, looks like something that belongs in a utility class (e.g. org/onap/cps/utils/DataMapUtils.java) and requires separate test!\n\n\nAlso would this inadvertently convert  real floats  like 1.0 to an int, how can we prevent that if we don't check the original String? I am not sure if this is the right solution...",
